data.description: #106 is and end unit with light shining in the extra windows! Concrete block walls between units insure quiet living.  New AC in 2023. New roof in process.  This super clean homeowner loves the paved patio and privacy of the preserve in the back with close access to a lovely boardwalk meandering through the Conservation area.   The Community Resort Style Pool and Spa are heated to enjoy year round. Tennis, volleyball and playground for active lifestyles. $95 monthly HOA includes all this plus mowing and irrigating your lawn. (even inside your private patio!) Multiple grocery stores, restaurants, shopping and bowling are within walking distance. Truly a Blue Zone Vibe! The upscale neighborhood is such a friendly walkable community hidden just off a dead end street so no through traffic. Beach is 15 minute drive! Historic Downtown Melbourne 10 minutes..
